QuestData.Title: The Al'ley Cat of Oribos
QuestData.Description:
Ah, Maw Walker. I have a message.
An individual has a proposition for you, specifically. I know nothing of the details, only that they asked you meet them towards the back of the Idyllia.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet with the mysterious contact in Oribos.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet with the mysterious contact in Oribos.
QuestData.RewardText: It is a pleasure to meet you.
